data.description: Welcome, this beautiful house has an enviable layout, it has three bedrooms and two full bathrooms and a study without carpet. It has a formal dining room with enough space, the kitchen is open so you can enjoy it at all times, in the back there is the main room with a separate shower and bathtub. Apart from that, it has a personalized closet to optimize the space perfectly. The house is located in the beautiful community of Water's Edge that has a clubhouse, parks, fitness center, pool and walking trails on the shores of the lake!!!
